# AWS CloudWatch Monitoring & Alerting Lab

## Overview
Configured monitoring and alerting for EC2 instances using 
Amazon CloudWatch and SNS notifications.

## What I Did
- Created CloudWatch alarm for EC2 CPU utilization
- Set threshold for high CPU
- Connected alarm to SNS topic
- Configured email subscription notification
- Tested alert by stress loading instance

## What I Learned
- Metrics vs logs
- EC2 performance monitoring
- Importance of proactive alerting
